### Loop & Bloom API - REST Client Test Suite

@base_url = http://localhost:8000
@content_type = application/json

### Variables (set after registration/login)
@access_token = 

---

## ==================== AUTH ENDPOINTS ====================

### Health Check
GET {{base_url}}/health

---

### Register User
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "full_name": "Test User",
  "password": "testpass123"
}

---

### Login
POST {{base_url}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

---

### Get Current User
GET {{base_url}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

## ==================== PRODUCT ENDPOINTS ====================

### Get All Products
GET {{base_url}}/api/products?skip=0&limit=10

---

### Get Product by ID
GET {{base_url}}/api/products/{product_id}

---

### Create Product (Admin)
POST {{base_url}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
  "name": "Custom Blanket",
  "description": "A beautiful custom crochet blanket",
  "price": 55.99,
  "image_url": "https://example.com/blanket.jpg",
  "stock": 5
}

---

### Update Product (Admin)
PUT {{base_url}}/api/products/{product_id}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
  "price": 59.99,
  "stock": 3
}

---

### Delete Product (Admin)
DELETE {{base_url}}/api/products/{product_id}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

## ==================== ORDER ENDPOINTS ====================

### Create Order
POST {{base_url}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "{product_id}",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 45.99
    }
  ],
  "shipping_address": "123 Main St, Springfield, IL 62701",
  "is_custom": false
}

---

### Get User Orders
GET {{base_url}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Get Order Details
GET {{base_url}}/api/orders/{order_id}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

## ==================== AI DESIGN ENDPOINTS ====================

### Generate AI Design
POST {{base_url}}/api/designs
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
  "prompt": "A cloud-shaped baby mobile in pastel pinks and whites",
  "style": "cute"
}

---

### Get User Designs
GET {{base_url}}/api/designs
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Get Design by ID
GET {{base_url}}/api/designs/{design_id}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

## ==================== ADMIN ENDPOINTS ====================

### Get All Orders (Admin)
GET {{base_url}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Get All Designs (Admin)
GET {{base_url}}/api/admin/designs
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Get All Users (Admin)
GET {{base_url}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

---

### Update Order Status (Admin)
PUT {{base_url}}/api/admin/orders/{order_id}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: {{content_type}}

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}
